race.comment: DALE (2) improved again narrowly beaten here and then tackled stronger grade at Rosehill and found it a bit rich over 1800m. The step up to the middle distance will be right up his alley and 3x winning rider Bullock is reunited. Sure to play a big role. CASINO STAGE (7) brings a 2.7L defeat from Dubbo over this distance but won easily at Mudgee prior. Tumbles in weight back a few levels and that brings him right into it. HAZE (3) improved last time out to score by 2 lengths over 1600m at this track. Maps for a soft run and also has a weight drop. Will get every chance to run out the extra journey. SEBILLA (4) seeks the hat-trick off a 66 win at Tamworth this trip and has been kept on the fresh side. Has an awkward gate but can feature again.
